
'''''Cook Off''''' ni filime yo gusetsa y'urukundo yo muri Zimbabwe yasohotse muri 2017 yanditswe kandi iyoborwa na Tomas Brickhill <ref>Cook Off (2017) - IMDb <nowiki>https://www.imdb.com</nowiki> › title</ref>.  film ikinamo Tendaiishe Chitima, Fungai Majaya na Tehn Diamond<ref>Cook Off, the no-budget romcom that became the first ... <nowiki>https://www.theguardian.com</nowiki> › world › may › cook-off...</ref> .  Gutunganya iyi filime byahoraga byibasirwa no kunanirwa kw'amashanyarazi, imbogamizi z’ingengo y’imari, imyigaragambyo yo kurwanya leta n’imvururu zadutse mu cyiciro cya nyuma cya Perezidansi ya Robert Mugabe<ref>Defying all odds: Zimbabwean romcom Cook Off makes Netflix ... <nowiki>https://www.aljazeera.com</nowiki> › economy › defying-all-od...</ref> . Yabaye filime ya mbere yasohotse muri Zimbabwe nyuma ya Mugabe yamaze imyaka igera kuri 40<ref>Zimbabwe romcom 'Cook Off' delights on Netflix debut - RFI <nowiki>https://www.rfi.fr</nowiki> › RFI › Africa</ref>.  Iyi filime kandi yabaye filime ya mbere ya Zimbabwe yerekanwe kuri Netflix<ref>Zimbabwe's Cook Off: How an $8000 romcom made it to Netflix <nowiki>https://www.bbc.com</nowiki> › news › world-africa-52983564</ref> .   Yitabiriwe n’itangazamakuru mpuzamahanga kuva yashyirwa ku rubuga rwa Netflix muri Kamena 2020<ref>'Cook Off' Zimbabwe's first movie on Netflix - FurtherAfrica <nowiki>https://furtherafrica.com</nowiki> › Africa</ref>.  Ni filime ya kabiri ya Zimbabwe yitabiriwe n’amahanga nyuma ya ''Neria''<ref>Film Review | Cook Off - New Frame <nowiki>https://www.newframe.com</nowiki> › film-review-cook-off</ref> .  Iyi filime irashimwa nka imwe muri filime nziza kurusha izindi zose muri Sinema ya Zimbabwe nyuma ya ''Neria'' na yellow Card kandi yafunguwe ku buryo bwiza cyane bwatanzwe n'Abanyazimbabwe<ref>Cook Off movie revives Zimbabwe's film muscle | The Chronicle <nowiki>https://www.chronicle.co.zw</nowiki> › cook-off-movie-revives-...</ref>. Iyi filime izwiho gusenya imyumvire y’inganda za firime zo muri Zimbabwe zari zamugaye kubera ibibazo by’ubukungu ndetse na hyperinflation muri iki gihugu.<ref>COOK OFF, fable zimbabwéenne à 8000 dollars - Films <nowiki>https://www.africavivre.com</nowiki> › films</ref> 

== Inyandiko ==
