== Gutanga ibihembo ==
Filime yakiriye ibihembo bike yanatoranijwe mubirori bya firime<ref>Zimbabwe's Award-Winning Film 'Cook Off' On Netflix Screens <nowiki>https://allafrica.com</nowiki> › stories</ref>. Yatwaye ibihembo bine byose mu birori bya firime, harimo bibiri buri kimwe mu iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Cambria 2020<ref>Cook Off | Cambria Film Festival 2020 <nowiki>https://cambriafilmfestival2020.eventive.org</nowiki> › schedule</ref>. na Zimbabwe International Film Festival.   Iyi filime kandi yahawe ibihembo bibiri by’ubuhanzi byatanzwe n’inama y’ubuhanzi ya Zimbabwe muri 2019<ref>WATCH: Award winning Zim romantic comedy to feature on ... <nowiki>https://www.glamour.co.za</nowiki> › lifestyle › glamour-guides</ref>.
